ep being nice and polite and say No. And I would smile a lot in my tells. Nothing seems to shut people down then you keep being nice and happy and just say &quot;No thank you <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> &quot; over and over. Anyway...not exactly what you are upset about...guess my point is everyone gets this in some form or another...and your best bet is to be honest and nice. Even to guildmates and friends. If they really are your friends they will understand you aren't a trick pony just their for their use. Only time I will always help is a CR...other then that...sorry my game time is just as valuable and for my enjoyment as the next players.  <p><b>Spring Starwind</b>
